description:
This is a modest collection (32) of the best super-car reviews and fastest Stig Power Laps from the British show Top Gear, chronologically listed.

They are high quality DIVX files, originally ripped by various torrent pirates, edited by aychberg.

If you want to watch all of the power laps in the order they were recorded, do not look at The Power Board, or it will do away with the suspense of watching the cars duke it out for #1 on the board.

